title: 919 out of 1,595 pass January 2017 architecture board exam
text:
By: Ed Margareth Barahan - @inquirerdotnet INQUIRER.net / 11:25 AM February 04, 2017 
A total of 919 out of 1,595 passed the January 2017 Architecture Licensure Examination, the Professional Regulation Commission (PRC) said on Friday. 
The licensure examination was administered in the cities of Manila, Baguio, Cebu, Davao and Legazpi last January 27 and 29, 2017. 
The results were released five working days after the last day of examination. ADVERTISEMENT 
The University of Santo Tomas topped the schools with 81.75 percent passing rate, while Luiz Marko Pantua Silang of University of the Philippines-Diliman ranked first in the list of successful examinees with a rating of 83.70 percent.
